---
title: Pasta and Chicken
image: pasta-and-chicken.jpg
---

Cook @pasta{500%g} until al dente, then drain.

Cut @chicken breast{500%g} into dices. Cook in a #pan{} with @chicken spices{}, @salt{}, and @garlic powder{} until golden and cooked through.

Peel and cube @potatoes{500%g}. Fry in @oil{200%ml} until golden and crispy.

Add @cooking cream{500%ml} to the chicken, stir, and let it simmer for a few minutes.

Add the potatoes and pasta, toss everything together, and serve.
